<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #102a43 0%, #243b53 100%);
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #102a43 0%, #243b53 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 40px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .logo-accent {
            color: #D4A017;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 35px 30px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p { margin: 0 0 16px 0; }
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            color: #666;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 3px solid #D4A017;
        }
        .footer-logo {
        }
        .footer-accent {
            color: #D4A017;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Kowihan<span class="logo-accent">Transit</span></div>
            <h1>Alerte Transport</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour,</p>
            <p>Nous souhaitons vous informer d'une perturbation :</p>
            <h3 style="color: #fa709a; margin: 20px 0;">{{subject}}</h3>
            <p>{{message}}</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Nous vous prions de nous excuser pour les désagréments occasionnés.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 25px;">Cordialement,<br><strong>L'équipe KowihanTransit</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-logo">Kowihan<span class="footer-accent">Transit</span></div>
            Ceci est un message automatique. Merci de ne pas y répondre.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>